text: Promyslovy () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tabun-Aralsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 38 km south-east from Yenotayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Promyslovy
